                <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-700 leading-relaxed">Mode Benar/Salah aktif. Opsi otomatis menjadi A (Benar) dan B (Salah).</p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mt-4 bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-100">
                <div class="key-standard flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400">KUNCI (PG/TF):</span>
                    <select class="key-input text-xs font-bold border-none bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded-lg px-3 py-1.5 shadow-sm outline-none"></select>
                </div>
                
                <div class="key-drag hidden w-full">
